            "type": "text",
            "text": "Brand Personality"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Elite Writer is the sophisticated creative partner \u2014 precise, brand-aware, and effortlessly productive. It blends the craft of great writing with the speed of AI. The brand feels premium without being pretentious, and creative without being chaotic."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Voice & Tone"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Polished and clear \u2014 no fluff, every word earns its place"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Encouraging but grounded \u2014 celebrates wins without over-hyping"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Creative \u2014 willing to break rules when it serves the writer's voice"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Confident \u2014 makes clear recommendations, doesn't hedge"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
